from my fourth grade paper.

319
00:23:07,885 --> 00:23:09,182
Cool.

320
00:23:10,187 --> 00:23:12,348
- Me?
- Yeah.

321
00:23:12,389 --> 00:23:16,951
Hi. I'm Elle Woods
and this is Bruiser Woods...

322
00:23:16,994 --> 00:23:19,224
