angora sweater.

330
00:23:37,681 --> 00:23:40,912
Whoever said orange was the new
pink was seriously disturbed.

331
00:23:46,356 --> 00:23:47,618
Wish me luck, Bruiser.

332
00:23:47,658 --> 00:23:50,627
This is my first class
as a serious law student.

333
00:23:56,934 --> 00:23:59,494
I totally look the part.

334
00:24:05,476 --> 00:24:07,740
There is no way
she got in here on her own.

335
00:24:36,006 --> 00:24:37,598
I totally forgot you go here.

336
00:24:37,641 --> 00:24:40,041
What are you talking about?

337
00:24:40,077 --> 00:24:42,511
I'm sorry.
Are you here to see me?

338
00:24:42,546 --> 00:24:45,538
No, silly. I go here.

339
00:24:45,582 --> 00:24:47,106
You go where?

340
00:24:47,150 --> 00:24:50,119
Harvard. Law school.

341
00:24:50,153 --> 00:24:53,054
You got into Harvard Law?

342
00:24:53,090 --> 00:24:55,024
What, like it's hard?

343
00:24:55,058 --> 00:24:57,390
Oh, my gosh, Warner,
it'll be so great.

344
00:24:57,427 --> 00:24:59,691
