I had never gone to Harvard.

454
00:32:49,898 --> 00:32:52,628
After you went
to all that trouble.

455
00:32:52,668 --> 00:32:54,192
He's engaged!

456
00:32:54,236 --> 00:32:56,397
She's got
the six-carat Harry Winston...

457
00:32:56,438 --> 00:32:58,998
on her bony, unpolished finger.

458
00:33:02,077 --> 00:33:04,011
