462
00:33:10,786 --> 00:33:13,448
"I met someone else.
Move out."

463
00:33:13,489 --> 00:33:17,016
Oh, no. That's awful.

464
00:33:17,059 --> 00:33:20,517
Dewey kept the trailer
and my precious baby Rufus.

465
00:33:23,765 --> 00:33:25,858
