a birthday party.

466
00:33:28,036 --> 00:33:30,470
What's a girl to do?

467
00:33:30,506 --> 00:33:32,599
He's a guy
who followed his pecker...

468
00:33:32,641 --> 00:33:34,609
to greener pastures...

469
00:33:34,643 --> 00:33:37,669
and I'm a middle-aged
high-school dropout...

470
00:33:37,713 --> 00:33:40,580
who's got stretch marks
and a fat ass.

471
00:33:40,616 --> 00:33:42,846
That's terrible.

472
00:33:42,885 --> 00:33:45,547
Yep. Happens every day.

473
00:33:47,422 --> 00:33:50,414
