483
00:34:20,655 --> 00:34:22,555
Look what I did.

484
00:34:22,590 --> 00:34:24,751
- See you later.
- Bye-bye, sugar.

485
00:34:26,794 --> 00:34:28,091
Aw, shit.

486
00:34:28,129 --> 00:34:31,565
Could I have been
any more goddamn spastic?

487
00:34:31,599 --> 00:34:33,089
It's OK.

488
00:34:34,502 --> 00:34:38,131
Are you sure this
Warner guy is, like, the one?

489
00:34:38,172 --> 00:34:41,300
Definitely. I love him.

490
00:34:44,445 --> 00:34:47,881
Well, if a girl like you
can't hold on to her man...

491
00:34:47,915 --> 00:34:51,681
then there sure as hell isn't
any hope for the rest of us.

492
00:34:53,020 --> 00:34:54,817
What are you waiting for?

493
00:34:56,757 --> 00:34:59,317
Steal the bastard back.

494
00:35:03,230 --> 00:35:03,764
I should warn you...

495
00:35:03,764 --> 00:35:04,389
I should warn you...

496
00:35:04,432 --> 00:35:06,366
that in addition to competing
against each other...

497
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:08,891
for the top grade
in this class...

498
00:35:08,936 --> 00:35:11,700
you will also be competing
for one of my firm's...

499
00:35:11,739 --> 00:35:15,470
highly coveted four
internship spots next year...

500
00:35:15,509 --> 00:35:19,172
where you will get to assist
on actual cases.

501
00:35:19,213 --> 00:35:22,182
Let the bloodbath begin.

502
00:35:23,351 --> 00:35:26,479
Now, let's commence
with our usual torture.

503
00:35:27,955 --> 00:35:30,583
Ms. Woods...

504
00:35:30,624 --> 00:35:33,184
would you rather have a client
who committed a crime...

505
00:35:33,227 --> 00:35:36,162
malum in se
or malum prohibitum?

506
00:35:39,900 --> 00:35:41,993
Neither.

507
00:35:42,036 --> 00:35:43,663
And why is that?

508
00:35:43,704 --> 00:35:47,037
I would rather have a client
who's innocent.

509
00:35:48,843 --> 00:35:51,812
Dare to dream, Ms. Woods.

510
00:35:54,648 --> 00:35:57,014
Ms. Kensington,
which would you prefer?

511
00:35:58,252 --> 00:35:59,685
Malum prohibitum.

512
00:36:01,489 --> 00:36:03,514
Because then the client
would have committed...

513
00:36:03,557 --> 00:36:07,357
a regulatory infraction as
opposed to a dangerous crime.

514
00:36:07,395 --> 00:36:10,057
Well done, Ms. Kensington.

515
